    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>While shopping for a new computer, I have found the young techies who assist in computer sales just seem to fog over when I try to explain the benefits of Word Perfect. It's nice to know I'm not the only one out there and that all the strange looks I have generated, even among my own friends, is not deserved.</p>
        <p>FRANCES ZEMANS  Chicago</p>
      </block>
